{"tid":521324,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 一齊玩揭尾故！25 之 happy birthday to ME","createTime":"2018-01-06T12:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T08:03:56.000Z","uid":136763,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"18179384b4252ac16cfad4f225163e4473e9647a","tid":521324,"uid":136763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T12:14:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的 馬田同小彤決定去哈爾濱旅行 <br />\n順便慶祝馬田生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出發前啲遊記話雪鄉好多嘢都劏遊客<br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n點解有兩個行李箱係地下嘅？ <br />\n<br />\n唔知呀 我地去玩啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n第二日 一個女人倒斃在雪鄉某客棧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打們 好耐無見 <br />\n無錯 過幾日的確係小弟牛一 <br />\n兼同小彤去哈爾濱旅行 <br />\n<br />\n順便作個揭尾故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來吧 出招吧！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20bd1301405761ec40aaa70f0b1b36fc22d65158","tid":521324,"uid":142316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"個女人係小彤？<br />\n死於意外？自殺？他殺？"},{"pid":"7051c490defa14887cbc5d3f535f63e5692d697b","tid":521324,"uid":136763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20bd1301405761ec40aaa70f0b1b36fc22d65158","tid":521324,"uid":142316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"個女人係小彤？<br />\n死於意外？自殺？他殺？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T12:19:55.000Z","msg":"不是<br />\n他殺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed4c0653003a03fa5accf224b6174372fba8855","tid":521324,"uid":142378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco